{
  "enabled": true,
  "version": "1",
  "name": "refactor-to-modular",
  "description": "将大文件重构为模块化结构",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Please help refactor a large file to modular structure:\n\n**Instructions**:\n1. Ask the user which file they want to refactor\n2. Use context-gatherer subagent to read the target file and analyze its structure\n3. Use context-gatherer subagent to read .kiro/docs/architecture/project-structure.md for modular architecture principles\n4. Based on the summaries, identify logical modules and suggest how to split into smaller files\n5. Provide a refactoring plan with file names and responsibilities\n\n**Follow KIRO-RULES.md**: Never directly use readFile. Always use context-gatherer subagent for reading project files and documentation.\n\nAsk the user which file they want to refactor, then proceed with the analysis."
  }
}
